APPEND return toplevel-flattened list
append list 1 2 3
  list 2 3 4
  list 5 list 6 7
(=> L:1 2 3 2 3 4 5 L:6 7)
pop L:1 2 3 2 3 4 5 L:6 7 (=> L:6 7)

PUSH atom to list
POP

